cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper presents a recognition and retrieval system for handwritten records using neural networks for optical character recognition. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as regular expressions are used to describe feasible word sequences. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the system retrieves information from historical handwritten records. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the system uses neural networks for optical character recognition. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the system uses machine learning techniques for recognition and retrieval.
